To compile

```
source compile.sh
then tun -> ./compile.sh

Compilation steps
	AaLinkExtMem    link aa files
	AaOpt           optimize aa
	Aa2VC           aa -> vc
	vc2vhdl         vc -> vhdl
	gcc             testbench compile
	ghdl            compile and elaborate

Simulation
	open tmux

	in one pane
		./maxoffour_system_test_bench

	in another pane
		./testbench_vhdl <a> <b> <c> <d>

Example
	./testbench_vhdl 10 20 5 15
```

To clean
source clean.sh
then tun -> ./clean.sh

Note
works with all inputs
check vhpi.log for output
